You can use capture and display filters, a capture filter is applied prior to capture, and will only capture what you filter and nothing else
a display filter - a filter used during an active capture or a precaptured packet.

Important thing to know: 
they are different and there are shortcuts for display filters.

Apply a display filter as "ftp" - FTP won't work but here you will capture other traffic as well.

Apply a capture filter as "tcp port 21" - select the correct interface 

