Shortcuts in Wireshark

TCP Display filter
1.) Click on a frame, select a property, right click on prepare a filter and you might see it there in display filter search bar== "tcp.dstport == 443"
2.) This time, select another property, right click on apply as filter and you might see it ran and can see the results.
